{"tid":1048372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK Yes 先達】撥5億推動中學IT創新實驗室　可買電話、平板電腦，行政費每年約1000萬","createTime":"2019-03-05T15:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T15:23:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"276d2fa161201629def6c7a8a59f54f311e81a8c","tid":1048372,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"政府上周三公布新一份財政預算案，提出撥款5億元推行「中學IT創新實驗室」計劃，在2019至2021學年向每間官津及直資中學提供最高100萬元資助，以提升校內資訊科技設備和設施，例如可<span style=\"color: red;\">購置平板電腦、智能手機</span>、無人機等。創新及科技局向立法會提交文件，指若建議獲通過，料在今年第二季向財委會提交撥款建議，年底前正式推出計劃<br />\n<br />\n為加強科普教育及「科學、科技、工程和數學」（STEM）教育，新一份財政預算案提出「中學IT創新實驗室」計劃，在2019至2021學年向每間官津及直資中學提供最高100萬元資助，以提升校內資訊科技設備和基礎設施，例如可購置光纖及寬頻網絡、雲端伺服、平板電腦、智能手機、無人機等。<br />\n<br />\n學校亦可舉辦相關的課外活動，例如人工智能編程班、虛擬實境工作坊等，以增加學生對人工智能、區塊鏈、雲端計算、大數據等認識。資助亦可作維修、教育支援的專業服務等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每年約1000萬行政費<br />\n</span><br />\n資科辦指，計劃屬自願性質，會盡量簡化申請及審批程序，並按學校提交的年度計劃書發放每年所需的款項。資科辦亦會成立諮詢委員會，擬備設備清單及審批學校申請。另外，計劃除涉5億元非經常開支外，每年有1,160萬元有時限經常開支，主要用作項目管理、資助計劃管理、諮詢委員會秘書處等開支。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/302444/%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%92%A55%E5%84%84%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8it%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%AE%A4-%E5%8F%AF%E8%B2%B7%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F302444%2F%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%2592%25A55%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8it%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%25AE%25A4-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6ee29014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/302444/%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88-%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%92%A55%E5%84%84%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8it%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%AE%A4-%E5%8F%AF%E8%B2%B7%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F</a>"},{"pid":"6e07f27e3a622411d0b76b07949747bd9b4ec64c","tid":1048372,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/f37675lo1f103.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ff37675lo1f103.png&h=3843b5ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ef2b48f853540d1b57417823cfad38e0021101a","tid":1048372,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e07f27e3a622411d0b76b07949747bd9b4ec64c","tid":1048372,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/f37675lo1f103.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ff37675lo1f103.png&h=3843b5ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見佢9up"},{"pid":"525ed7846a3279f27dd6b7f1a500525b9b771fbe","tid":1048372,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ed04f1424a2e964d4f3359d3b841bd0dd4b719","tid":1048372,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"買返黎 D 野都係成品，創咩新科技？"},{"pid":"2f763d4cfd3153dbc3a63881357d998492b813ec","tid":1048372,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03ed04f1424a2e964d4f3359d3b841bd0dd4b719","tid":1048372,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"買返黎 D 野都係成品，創咩新科技？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"比學生見識下美帝創新科技下產物<img src=\"/asset